Package: metacrawlr
Type: Package
Title: Extract and export dataset metadata from various data publication systems.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Marius", "Bottin",
      email = "mbottin@humboldt.org.co",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Metacrawlr allows to extract dataset metadata coming from variable list in xml format, or in database.
    For now, we considered the cases of IPT, Geonetwork and Dataverse publication systems.
